1. https://stepik.org/lesson/Стек-вызовов-538/step/8?unit=861
Ответ:
unsigned gcd(unsigned a, unsigned b)
{
    if(b == 0)
    {
        return a;
    }
    else
    {
        return gcd(b, a % b);
    }
}

